<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>CSS Selectors Example</title>

    <style>
        /* Element Selector */
        p {
            color: blue;
        }

        /* Class Selector */
        .highlight {
            color: green;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* ID Selector */
        #unique {
            color: red;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        /* Group Selector */
        h1, h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: purple;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <h1>CSS Selectors Demo</h1>
    <h2>Different Types of Selectors</h2>

    <p>This paragraph uses element selector.</p>

    <p class="highlight">
        This paragraph uses class selector.
    </p>

    <p id="unique">
        This paragraph uses id selector.
    </p>

</body>
</html>
